  <h2 id="opportunity-attributes-5" class="govuk-heading-m app-summary-list-heading">Skills and experience</h2>
  
  <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3">Buyers will use the essential and nice-to-have skills and experience to help them evaluate suppliers’ technical competence.</p>
  
  

  

  
<dl class="govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list--top-border govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Essential skills and experience
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>Track record of working as an Agile Coach</li>
          <li>Strong understanding of Scrum and Kanban</li>
          <li>Experience as a Scrum master or with the agile methodology</li>
          <li>Working with Agile in the public sector and familiarity with GDS/Digital First standards</li>
          <li>Knowledge of agile software development</li>
          <li>Demonstrable evidence of strong communication and problem-solving skills with demonstrable evidence interpersonal skills and patience</li>
          <li>In addition to above, please send CV to DS_PMO_Mailbox@disclosurescotland.gov.scot by 12pm on 12th April 2021</li>
        </ul>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Nice-to-have skills and experience
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
</dl>

  <h2 id="opportunity-attributes-6" class="govuk-heading-m app-summary-list-heading">How suppliers will be evaluated</h2>
  
  <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3">All suppliers will be asked to provide a work history.</p>
  
  

  

  

  

  
<dl class="govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list--top-border govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          How many specialists to evaluate
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          5
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Cultural fit criteria
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>Be transparent and collaborative whilst working</li>
          <li>Have a no-blame culture and encourage people to learn from their mistakes</li>
          <li>Take responsibility for their work</li>
          <li>Share knowledge and experience with other team members</li>
          <li>Challenge the status quo</li>
          <li>Be comfortable standing up for their discipline</li>
          <li>Be comfortable with working with clients with both high and low technical expertise</li>
        </ul>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Additional assessment methods
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Evaluation weighting
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-0 govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Technical competence</p>
        <div>60%</div>
        <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3 govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Cultural fit</p>
        <div>20%</div>
        <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-top-3 govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Price</p>
        <div>20%</div>
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
</dl>

  </div>
</div>
<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-full">
    

<h2 id="clarification-questions" class="govuk-heading-m app-summary-list-heading">Questions asked by suppliers</h2>



  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  

  
<dl class="govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list--top-border govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          1. IR35 status?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Off-payroll working rules (IR35) do not apply so outside IR35.     A copy of the Gov.uk determination can be provided if required.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          2. RE : Essential skills and experience - In addition to above, please send CV to DS_PMO_Mailbox@disclosurescotland.gov.scot by 6th April 2021
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Please submit CV&#39;s by Tuesday 6th April at 11:59pm GMT.<br>Please ensure that you also complete the skills and experience spreadsheet to allow your application via the DOS system to be accepted
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          3. Earliest Start date:
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          We would like someone to start as soon as they have BPSS clearance.   <br>Once supplier informs us that BPSS clearance is complete, we would arrange for a laptop to be picked up from the office (or delivered to you if not local).
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          4. Number of days required?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          3 days a week.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          5. Is there a current incumbent ?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          No incumbent.  Plenty of Agile experienced technical staff, however Agile Coach is a new role for DS.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          6. Is the 3-days/week flexible? For example, one week could be two days and the following week 4 days?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          We try to be as flexible as possible, however it would be dependent on business needs.     This would be discussed further on an individual basis.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          7. What is the target start date?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Looking for someone to start as soon as they have BPSS clearance.   We would take into account notice periods, but the sooner the better.   This can be discussed on a individual basis should you pass the initial sift.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          8. Any idea on target rate for this opportunity?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          We do not have a target rate.   We would like to see how the market responds.   Rates are taken into account after CV/response sifts at the procurement evaluation stage.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          9. Email of CV listed as an essential requirement. Date 6th of April this would be before shortlisting has even begun as this is the closing date of your published opportunity. We would not expect you to ask for a CV until the second stage (evaluation) after you have shortlisted the suppliers.
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          We find a CV is valuable in this process.   We have requested this as such.<br>If you do not wish to submit a CV, please ensure your responses are fully detailed.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          10. The latest start date states 3rd April 2021, however application closing date is listed as 6th April 2021. Please can you clarify.
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Ideally would like someone to start as soon as they have BPSS clearance.  An early May start date is likely but the sooner the better.<br>Once supplier informs us that BPSS clearance is complete, we would arrange for a laptop to be picked up from the office (or delivered to you if not local).
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          11. Is there an incumbent in this role?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          No incumbent. Plenty of Agile experienced technical staff, however Agile Coach is a new role for DS.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          12. How many CV’s can we submit?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          One from each supplier
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          13. Whats the max day rate for this role?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          We do not have a max rate figure. We would like to see how the market responds. <br><br>Rates are taken into account after CV/response sifts at the procurement evaluation stage.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          14. Will remote working remain for the duration of the contract or is there an expectation to return to in person working practices post COVID restrictions being lifted?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Scottish Government has not finalised it&#39;s return to work policy.   It&#39;s unlikely that we will be back in the office until after the summer.    When we do, it is likely we will only be in the office for specific meetings and the default will be work from home.   This however, cannot be confirmed just now.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          15. Please could you please provide a max charge rate or a budget for this assignment?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          We do not have a max rate figure. We would like to see how the market responds.<br><br>Rates are taken into account after CV/response sifts at the procurement evaluation stage.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          16. Would the contracted resource be able to work for other clients in-between working for Disclosure Scotland.
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Yes, expectation is 3 days per week for this contract.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          17. Would the contracted resource be able to work for other clients in-between working for Disclosure Scotland (as this is a 3 day a week contract?)
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Yes, expectation is 3 days per week for this contract.  No restrictions on working for other clients.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          18. Can the contractor work more than 3 days per week?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          We are looking for a 3 day a week resource.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          19. Should those who can only work remotely due to being located outside Scotland and unable to travel to the clients offices not apply?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          No, please apply.  We can discuss individual circumstances if applications are progressed.   The role is likely to remain remote for a good while yet.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          20. Following on from your answer to Q14, would the buyer be prepared to cover expenses for the in person meetings if and when required?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          This role will not have expenses as part of the contract.   We would be unable to pay travel expenses.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          21. Interviews are not listed as one of the assessment methods. Will interviews be undertaken during the evaluation phase, if shortlisted?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          We do not plan to hold scored interviews.<br>We may hold calls with applicants for clarification of information but this will not be scored.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          22. The specification refers to an individual coach but would you also consider a team approach?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          We would prefer an individual as the post is 3 days a week and costed for 1 person.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          23. Can you describe how you will measure success? What do you expect to be different in 12 months?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          We are looking for a coach to:<br>Train teams on agile methodology. Oversee development of agile teams to ensure effective outcomes for DS.<br><br>Guide teams and encouraging them to embrace the agile method.<br><br>Arm teams with the right knowledge, tools and training to use agile to its full potential.<br><br>The success will be when these can be clearly seen as active in DS.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
</dl>



